          <p>"The guide made choices easy — picked one from each step and got started."</p>
          <div class="ml-testimonial-author">&mdash; H., Sharjah</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {%- comment -%} ── SHIPPING / TRUST ── {%- endcomment -%}
    <section aria-label="Shipping and trust">
      <span class="ml-kicker">Nootropix advantage</span>
      <h2 class="ml-heading">Fast. Local. Reliable.</h2>
      <div class="ml-trust-grid">
        <div class="ml-trust-item">
          <span class="ml-trust-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#9889;</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Lightning delivery</strong>
            <span class="ml-trust-detail">Within Dubai: ~4 hours in city limits. Rest of UAE: same or next day. International express available.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ml-trust-item">
          <span class="ml-trust-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#128666;</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Fair shipping</strong>
            <span class="ml-trust-detail">Free UAE shipping on orders &ge; 300 AED. Simple and transparent.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ml-trust-item">
          <span class="ml-trust-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#128260;</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Easy returns</strong>
            <span class="ml-trust-detail">Unopened items returnable within 3 days. Your satisfaction matters.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {%- comment -%} ── FAQ (animated disclosure) ── {%- endcomment -%}
    <section aria-label="Frequently asked questions">
      <span class="ml-kicker">Questions</span>
      <h2 class="ml-heading">Memory &amp; Learning FAQ</h2>

      {% if faq_blocks.size > 0 %}
        {% for block in faq_blocks %}
          <details class="ml-faq" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
            <summary class="ml-faq-q">{{ block.settings.q }}<span class="ml-faq-chevron" aria-hidden="true"></span></summary>
            <div class="ml-faq-answer"><div class="ml-faq-inner"><p>{{ block.settings.a }}</p></div></div>
          </details>
        {% endfor %}
      {% else %}
        <details class="ml-faq">
          <summary class="ml-faq-q">Will this keep me up at night?<span class="ml-faq-chevron" aria-hidden="true"></span></summary>
          <div class="ml-faq-answer"><div class="ml-faq-inner"><p>None of these are stimulants in the traditional sense, but timing matters. Take earlier in the day and keep caffeine moderate.</p></div></div>
        </details>
        <details class="ml-faq">
